data.description: Welcome to your serene 3 bedroom, 2 bath retreat nestled in the picturesque Sanger Foothills! This enchanting riverfront home offers the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility. Step inside to discover a spacious living area adorned with natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances and ample counter space, making meal preparation a delight. Outside, the beauty of nature awaits on your expansive 1.66-acre property. Enjoy breathtaking views of the river, perfect for morning coffee or evening cocktails. A two-car garage provides convenience, while a charming small barn offers additional storage or workshop space. Immerse yourself in the lush landscape surrounding the home, where verdant lawns and mature trees provide a serene backdrop for outdoor activities and leisurely strolls. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or an idyllic setting for entertaining, this riverfront oasis offers the quintessential California lifestyle you've been dreaming of. Come experience the magic of Sanger Foothills living!
